oupling between magnetism and ferroelectricity\nmediated by structural distortions, which will be useful for the future\napplications of multiferroics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 17:59:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Jul 2018 18:27:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-09"}
