ption that the AzTEC sources are at the redshift of\nthe central radio galaxy, the misalignment reported here can be interpreted as\nSMGs preferentially inhabiting mass-dominant filaments funneling material\ntowards the protoclusters, which are also the parent structures of the radio\ngalaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jun 2018 04:23:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-11"}
